messageBody:
Hi all,

I had questions about JRefactory that maybe someone can answer...

If I try to rename a method, that option is dimmed out. Has anyone
seen this? Do I have something setup wrong?

I've also seen this for rename class. I did one rename of a class and
it worked, but when I tried this on the second class it was dimmed
out. I tried reloading the UML and creating a new UML dwg. I
tried rebuilding the app, but I still cannot do this operation.

I'm using JBuilder4, JDK 1.3, and JRefactory 2.5.38.

If there is another list that is more appropriate for this message,
please
send me a note and I repost elsewhere.

Thanks in advance.
